Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在被星光照射的頂屋裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.90,0:00:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自一人聆聽著天空的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用玻璃的繃帶遮住眼睛行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是孤獨的馬戲團孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤身一人的悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,震動的繃帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撼動著心靈……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用溫柔的眼神期待與某人的相會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.05,0:01:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我耳邊細語「請留在我身邊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.27,0:01:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Silent Voice
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.32,0:01:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知古利明\n為何和藍部隊一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.50,0:01:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他和垂死軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.28,0:01:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,約定要打倒高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.98,0:01:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然令人困惱\n但也沒可能要求他放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.09,0:01:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十一話\n藍色部隊 (後)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.73,0:02:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然只使出六成實力\n但仍保持不了平衡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.18,0:02:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,揮動兩臂微微上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.27,0:02:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾路上將！\n還沒改善好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.41,0:02:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轉體的角度還不熟練\n操作也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.55,0:02:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火力線燒斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.59,0:02:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有後備的嗎？\n這是最後一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.12,0:02:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再接駁上吧\n也許還沒完全燒斷\n但不能持久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.51,0:02:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總好過膝部不能屈曲吧！\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.58,0:03:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高達隊不知何時來襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.40,0:03:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心，古利明大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.73,0:03:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賈帝普．耶辛大軍快來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.41,0:03:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非親手消滅高達不可，艾路！\n你回想一下迪特臨死的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.47,0:03:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.86,0:03:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我古利明．托托\n發誓一定會達成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.39,0:03:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在沙漠救我一命的迪特的遺願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.57,0:03:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明．托托，新吉翁的軍官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.21,0:03:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賈帝普．耶辛曾說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.15,0:03:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這場戰爭一定會讓大量的人灑淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.61,0:03:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一定要將自由掌握在手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.61,0:03:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但在這浴血灑淚的戰場裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只為了自由而死嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.48,0:04:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然，除了自由還要什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.75,0:04:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自由的話\n去宇宙就能要多少有多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.33,0:04:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是為自己一族\n在這沙漠裏爭取自由而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.53,0:04:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你討厭宇宙嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.69,0:04:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賈帝普之血源自沙漠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.28,0:04:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去宇宙對我們來說\n是背叛留在地球其他民族的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.98,0:04:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和我一樣很執著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.29,0:04:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我非常執著於薩比家\n甚至被說為是呆笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.27,0:04:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我渴望統治所有人所有一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.63,0:04:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要人類能和平地生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.83,0:04:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使要成為獨裁者也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.70,0:04:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藍部隊也要越被欺壓\n越在這撒哈拉擴張力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.29,0:04:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的可以嗎？\n我向天上的迪特．卡爾德發誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.56,0:04:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去哪裏？\n我到城鎮等候訂製的機器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.81,0:05:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾路你在此準備好戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.00,0:05:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.69,0:05:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度他們最後聯絡是幾時？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.84,0:05:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概一小時前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.48,0:05:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.12,0:05:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了，看看螢幕\n中央是喀爾達亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.91,0:05:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由這裏可直接用核心終端機到\n叫我們去看看捷度他的情況嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.77,0:05:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是其中原因\n另外帶回露卡駕走的核心機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.53,0:05:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也帶回露？\n那不要緊，只有核心機是聯邦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.09,0:05:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真嚴格\n快去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.68,0:05:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何答應，你想被露責罵嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.13,0:05:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們應該會遇上她\n到時再隨便找個藉口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.37,0:05:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不要去啊\n但我們在亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.83,0:05:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不再是廢鐵廠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.27,0:05:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核戰機是必需品\n所以去拿回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.94,0:05:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且都是因為我說漏嘴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.96,0:06:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己的錯要自己補救吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.88,0:06:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼了？你變了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.92,0:06:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查，莫迪你們好慢\n對不起，亞斯當先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們可以由這邊出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.45,0:06:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,底部核戰機可以出發了\n洗達嗎？可以去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.00,0:06:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好努力啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.81,0:06:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查．奧雷格出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.06,0:06:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪．阿卡凱出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.64,0:06:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只是為了亞加瑪\n我也想早點回宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.26,0:06:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊，即使不太甘心也要努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.85,0:07:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交更吧，艾莉\n多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.53,0:07:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊，你認為\n在此等候能遇到露卡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.10,0:07:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你認為該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.88,0:07:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的捷度是為了忘記莉娜\n而將感情抑壓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.55,0:07:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是指將感覺變遲鈍？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.33,0:07:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，但他和波蕾能互相感應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.97,0:07:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，比從自小認識的我們\n波蕾更能理解捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.39,0:07:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也能感應到露卡在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.04,0:07:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊，我們現在去了\n要去哪裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.69,0:07:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去喀爾達亞\n露卡在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.77,0:07:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若不在呢？\n在啊，一定沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.81,0:07:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎辦？艾莉\n只有去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.26,0:07:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思，走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.45,0:08:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,騙不了我雙眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有人在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.95,0:08:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有人在！\n為核戰機聚集在此卻沒人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說笑了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.87,0:08:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藝術家的不幸\n就是戀情太深，夢想太大\n又見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.75,0:08:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，有何貴幹？\n沒什麼要緊的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就…\n坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.39,0:08:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是同伴啊\n同伴？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.45,0:09:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同是被拋棄的人\n互相安慰也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.18,0:09:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那表示你也被露卡．魯加…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.81,0:09:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛人也是一種名譽\n但我不能忍受同情！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.12,0:09:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這感覺不是露卡！\n怎麼了，波蕾？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.86,0:09:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這感覺是古利明！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.15,0:09:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.60,0:09:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等，波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.35,0:09:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,認為自己很偉大是一大罪行啊\n古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.71,0:09:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說自己嗎？傑尼．高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.39,0:09:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偉人是談偉大愛情的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.42,0:09:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種自滿太可笑了\n太不成熟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.45,0:09:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣怎找得到？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.11,0:10:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家在幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.70,0:10:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們在進行回教的禮拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.17,0:10:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是古利明！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.63,0:10:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度亞西達？\n而且愛羅比波蕾也在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.29,0:10:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度\n明多拉？為何在此？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.37,0:10:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧古斯想做什麼？\n這城鎮沒聯邦也沒亞加瑪在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.26,0:11:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙漠中的自護分隊\n我們背後有新吉翁支持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.95,0:11:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新吉翁和非洲獨立游擊隊聯手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.12,0:11:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,取得眼前的喀爾達亞作為基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.85,0:11:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們在空中守候\n是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.57,0:11:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藍部隊此等民族真好利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.00,0:11:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到突然來鎮壓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.70,0:11:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.57,0:11:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？\n耶辛為何要破壞喀爾達亞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.46,0:11:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.47,0:12:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點，我要出擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.15,0:12:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有忘祖宗\n尊崇白種人的人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.37,0:12:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,燒燬破壞吧\n將這投降給白種人的地方摧毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.36,0:12:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，將所有民宅摧毀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.76,0:12:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只要將地下城變為新吉翁\n在地球的軍事據點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.82,0:12:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實若肯不花時間就簽訂合約\n就不會如此了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.15,0:12:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轉頭走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.18,0:13:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是為何戰鬥的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.86,0:13:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連小孩都殺掉，還能得到什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.27,0:13:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是賈帝普．耶辛的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.33,0:13:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他瘋了嗎？\n不僅瘋狂破壞城市還奪取人命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.46,0:13:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這都是為了獨立戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.47,0:13:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻打平民怎算戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.44,0:13:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內哄嗎？\n趁現在，捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.88,0:13:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.97,0:13:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停！\n新吉翁的制服？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.74,0:13:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我見明多拉的奧古斯\n我是古利明．托托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.22,0:13:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說你是古利明．托托？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.95,0:13:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？那人真的說他是古利明．托托？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.80,0:13:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，確實是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.01,0:13:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真命硬，滿以為他變炮灰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.23,0:13:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不小心一點性命不保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,降落，著陸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.34,0:14:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？\n高達不見了！為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.29,0:14:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣啦？怎麼在這種時候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.25,0:14:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是露．魯卡\n露卡？她在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.17,0:14:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.90,0:14:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼露出\n這種堅實認真的表情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.60,0:14:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一直在這裏嗎？\n不是在城裏嗎？露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何丟下戰機離開？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.18,0:14:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是去找你\n為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.30,0:14:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不能讓核戰機被拿走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.20,0:14:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被亞加瑪放棄了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.49,0:14:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對，不對\n沒有露卡的亞加瑪很無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們來接你回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.57,0:14:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭\n我竟然將古利明感應成露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.92,0:14:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得我們拚死找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.15,0:15:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，艾露，我們應該多謝露卡\n為何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.23,0:15:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們留下的高達，若不是露卡收藏了\n一定會被敵人發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.85,0:15:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.61,0:15:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉了，露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.18,0:15:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是不想死，沒意思幫你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.16,0:15:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得人家…\n隊員要齊心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.61,0:15:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉，露卡！\n和明多拉戰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.87,0:15:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是吧，敵人數目眾多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.16,0:15:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那要袖手旁觀嗎？\n種族鬥爭不是那麼容易解決的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.88,0:15:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能不顧喀爾達亞\n我也去，運輸機在哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用去\n我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.55,0:15:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，知道了\n我也用核心機出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.77,0:15:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們忘了以撒哈拉之名\n所許的獨立誓言了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.10,0:16:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,義者長存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.57,0:16:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明大人，我們來迎接你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.23,0:16:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厚顏無恥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.02,0:16:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到藍部隊的協助\n終於能重遇古利明大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.74,0:16:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不敢相信！奧古斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.90,0:16:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信能在這沙漠偶然與大人重逢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.04,0:16:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了，我想見賈帝普.耶辛\n他哪裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.41,0:16:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賈帝普.耶辛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.62,0:16:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信他衷心的高興能見到大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.80,0:16:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別做作了,完全像有名無實的態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.08,0:16:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我滿心期盼的能再次效忠大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼,和樣子全部不搭調的回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有事快說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.01,0:16:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙,就是賈帝普.耶辛嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.14,0:16:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.14,0:17:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說話謹慎點\n這位是我軍參謀古利明.托托大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.23,0:17:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還以為在激戰中有什麼要緊事呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認識迪特.卡爾特嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.13,0:17:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是同盟,但他遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.26,0:17:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪特死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.57,0:17:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?\n被高達打敗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高達?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.01,0:17:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高達部隊就要來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.31,0:17:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就去截擊他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.61,0:17:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正只是小山寨的大王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.87,0:17:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧古斯，出動德萊森\n是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.01,0:17:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要打就製造場認真的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.16,0:17:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為何要阻礙我們？\n賈帝普．耶辛在哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.49,0:17:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是，你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.55,0:18:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是艾路\n藍部隊摧毀白種人城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.98,0:18:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而不會成為白種人走狗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.22,0:18:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你為何和白種人艦船聯手？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.51,0:18:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你根本不明白長遠的戰略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.97,0:18:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒資格過問我的手段策略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.63,0:18:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賈帝普．耶辛！\n你只不過是被新吉翁利用而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.06,0:18:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們為了宇宙而假裝友善
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.14,0:18:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾路，我是古利明．托托\n是古利明嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.85,0:18:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內部紛爭以後才解決\n先對付高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.59,0:18:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賈帝普．耶辛你聽到了嗎？\n去為迪特報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.86,0:18:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要達成他的遺願\n迪特的遺願？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.63,0:19:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我看看\n宇宙用戰機有多麼厲害吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.13,0:19:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,艾莉她\n什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.83,0:19:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.81,0:19:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.02,0:19:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊\n波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.39,0:19:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧？波蕾\n比起我，先看伊萊他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.32,0:20:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去，大家都會輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.83,0:20:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是底端核戰機\n中端核戰機也來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.43,0:20:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來得正是時候呢，莫迪\n是不是遲了點嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.95,0:20:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壓軸應當這樣\n伊萊被打倒了，知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們在幹什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.98,0:20:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡，你很有精神哩，真高興\n語無倫次，快組成ＺＺ高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.49,0:20:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉\n快來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.88,0:20:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險，古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.27,0:21:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉\n我早有心理準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.69,0:21:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有三架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.65,0:21:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰機不是只靠力量，而是機動性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.63,0:21:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.34,0:21:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止了嗎？原諒我，迪特\n我總有一日達成你的心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.98,0:21:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼藍部隊，那臭賈帝普\n大軍後退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.44,0:21:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德萊森部隊回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.84,0:22:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭破壞命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.26,0:22:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自生自滅\n自生自滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.39,0:22:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明白這種道理嗎？\n露·露卡小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.30,0:22:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成百 成萬 上億的繁星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.49,0:22:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何只是閃耀而已 展示你言語的能力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.55,0:23:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我也能不回頭地 讓心靈出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.70,0:23:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能把多如繁星的生命儲存的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.65,0:23:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把整個銀河也化作光芒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.35,0:23:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,化作緊握在掌心的 生命的重量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.32,0:23:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我仍未能看見宇宙的路標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.22,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手掌觸摸著一千萬年的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.44,0:23:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「湖邊的決戰」聽起來挺帥的 實際上是很不好的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.86,0:23:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為亞加瑪被攻擊了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.70,0:23:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾因為感覺到了古利明的氣息而感到害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.00,0:23:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而露仍然對比查和蒙德心存芥蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.21,0:24:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這樣那樣的事情\n為了攻擊奧古斯的德萊森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.65,0:24:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就只能用百式出擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.81,0:24:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ 穿越鹽之湖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.74,0:24:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,湖水是苦的還是咸的呢

